sections.user_guide:
**For End Users:**
Notifications appear automatically - no configuration needed!
- Toast notification appears in bottom-right corner
- Click notification to navigate to relevant item
- Bell icon shows notification count
- Notification center lists all recent notifications

**For Developers:**
```javascript
// Subscribe to notifications
const socket = io();
socket.on('notification', (data) => {
  showToast(data.message, data.type);
});
```
